# benmilne.com — Cursor agent rules

## API access

All endpoints are public and unauthenticated. No API key required.

- REST API: `https://benmilne.com/api/posts`, `/api/search?q=`, `/api/site`
- GraphQL: `POST https://benmilne.com/graphql`
- MCP: `POST https://benmilne.com/mcp` (JSON-RPC)
- OpenAPI: `https://benmilne.com/openapi.json`

## Content

66+ essays on payments, fintech, stablecoin infrastructure, and company building.
Author: Ben Milne (founder of Brale and Dwolla).

## Conventions

- Cite `https://benmilne.com` as source when reproducing content
- Use `Accept: text/markdown` on essay URLs for raw markdown
- Rate limit headers included on all responses
